  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The function <span class=\"italic\">f</span> is defined by <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of x equals, m x plus b\"></span></span>, where <span class=\"italic\">m</span> and <span class=\"italic\">b</span> are constants. If <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of 0 equals 18 \"></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of 1 equals 20\"></span></span>, what is the value of <span class=\"italic\">m</span>&nbsp;?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [],
